Description
fr.cnrs.iees.omugi
omugi stands for "One More Ultimate Graph Implementation".
fr.cnrs.iees.omugi.collections.tables
Interfaces and implementing classes for multi-dimensional data that can be used as node and edge attributes in graphs.

The core interfaces of the omugi library: graph, node, edge, etc.
fr.cnrs.iees.omugi.graph.impl
Three implementations of the fr.cnrs.iees.omugi.graph interfaces.
fr.cnrs.iees.omugi.graph.io
Interfaces for graph importation from / exportation to text files.
fr.cnrs.iees.omugi.graph.io.impl
Implementations of GraphExporter and GraphImporter for various data formats.
fr.cnrs.iees.omugi.graph.property
Basic classes to store attributes (here called properties) of any type in graph elements (nodes and edges).

fr.cnrs.iees.omugi.identity.impl
Implementation classes for interfaces of fr.cnrs.iees.omugi.identity.
fr.cnrs.iees.omugi.io
Classes to import / export graphs into data files of various formats.
fr.cnrs.iees.omugi.io.parsing

fr.cnrs.iees.omugi.io.parsing.impl
Implementing classes for interfaces of fr.cnrs.iees.omugi.io.parsing.
